Description: Model Context Protocol SDK for Python 3
 The MCP Python SDK implements the Model Context Protocol for Python-based
 clients and servers.
 .
 It provides typed request and response models, stdio and HTTP-capable client
 and server transports, FastMCP helpers, and a command-line interface for
 development and validation workflows.
 .
 This packaging currently assumes python3-typing-inspection is available in
 the target archive.
